DISTRIBUTION.—Species of the genus have been reported from central, eastern and southeastern Asia with records from Bhutan , China , India , Indochina, Indonesia , Japan , Malaya, Myanmar , Nepal , Pakistan , Ryukyu Islands, Sri Lanka , Taiwan , Thailand , Tibet, and Vietnam ( Metcalf 1963 ; Duffels and van der Laan 1986; Sanborn 2013 ; 2015 ; Price et al. 2016 ;
Price et al . 2019
